3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication channels and multiple-access channels, which are networking concepts. 
4. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper deals with the Gaussian two-way wire-tap channel, which is a signal processing problem. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with communication channels, which can be related to multimedia communication.
